---
title: Almond-Crusted Chicken Thighs with Creamy Mash
description: Making crispy, almond- and panko-coated chicken is surprisingly easy when you follow our simple steps. The end result? Crunchy, savoury chicken served with a creamy potato mash and garlicky broccoli.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/hauts-de-cuisse-de-poulet-en-croute-damandes-8ae585cd.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/almond-crusted-chicken-thighs-64d27786f9ec299950029571-14c37b60.pdf
